movie-description: Commander Craig-Scott of the Laundry Corps is thrust into command of his space ship when the senior officers die. With the help of Laundry Chief Blather, he stuggles to give his daily reports.
movie-short-description: Directed by Jon-Michael Preece.  With Tiffani Timms, Sophie Banks, Gerard Fasel, Greg Anderson. Commander Craig-Scott of the Laundry Corps is thrust into command of his space ship when the senior officers die. With the help of Laundry Chief Blather, he stuggles to give his daily reports.
